  <summary date="2017-01-30T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Rural Hospital Regulatory Relief Act of 2017

This bill amends title XVIII (Medicare) of the Social Security Act to permanently extend the application by the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services of an instruction&#160;against&#160;the enforcement of&#160;certain physician supervision requirements with respect to outpatient therapeutic services in critical access hospitals and small rural hospitals.</summary>
